						               													<description>Your mission in the game of Revolt is to find out which players are your sworn enemies and destroy them! Be cautious however, as teams will change in the blink of an eye. Use your cards wisely to gain information about the other players, slay your opponents, betray your allies, and hasten the Revolt!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The goal of Revolt is to determine which of the other players are on your team and slay your enemies.  However, teams are hidden at the beginning and will change throughout the duration of the game. You need to use your memory, induction, and political machinations to achieve victory.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Use cards from your hand to slay opponents, betray your allies, forge an alliance with your enemies, steal other players cards, and stop other players from using their cards.  You may play as many cards from your hand as you would like on each of your turns.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is won when all the players left alive agree that they are on the same team. They then reveal their team to all players.  If they are correct, victory is achieved. However, if they are wrong, all living players are dead and all other players are alive and gameplay continues.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
